Would recommend and come back to try more of their vegan options.", 'rating': '4', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': 'So thrilled to see yet another fabulous vegan eaterie in France. I had the green fish burger and it had a fabulous texture!  Topped with tartare in a brioche bun why do we even need to risk people lives in order to plunder our oceans?!!🤷🏼‍♀️. Just lovely, lovely, lovely. If you’re vegan or not then get your butts in this establishment as there’s a great choice.', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': 'We were in a hurry to the Moulin Rouge after missing a dinner reservation. The server fit us in and got our food in time! The burgers were beyond delicious! And the service was phenomenal! Definitely recommend', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': 'One of the best vegan burgers ever! If you feed this to a non vegetarian, for sure he will not notice 🤫

I got the chichen burger and I loved it! Onion rings were too greasy though.
The truffle mayo sauce was wow!

It’s great that this place is open even between lunch and dinner when many restaurants close. 🎉', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}]

name: Rice & Burger Kitchen
reviews: [{'author': '', 'text': "Excellent value for money. The Rice & Bolo and Cheddar fries are excellent. We came back twice during our short stay in Paris.\nThe Owner speaks perfectly English and is fun to talk to, sadly I didn't catch his name", 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': 'Amazing! Lovely staff, lovely service, super kind and super quick. Delicious burger and fries, really affordable. Will be back and will pass the word on! Merci :)', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': 'This place is truly amazing and unbeatable! I basically tried most of the food and i just love them all. The owner and staff are very kind, friendly and well serviced. My favorite is Rice & Bolo, the pilons ( they’re massive ) and double cheese burger! Also the price is insaneeee, definitely the best student option in Paris. If there’s 10 starts, I would give it a 10. Highly recommended !!', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': 'Bah we can call it street food but good quality great price and the service 1000/10 the guy at the window is always charismatic but let’s be honest would be better with space to actually dine-in but still you have to visit', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': 'The food is always  fresh   and   test is amazing ..   👌', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}]

name: Marvely
reviews:
[{'author': '', 'text': 'The food was amazing! We don’t speak French and our server spoke enough English to help. I would recommend this place to anyone traveling to Paris. I’m already wanting to return to try something else!', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': "Hello brunchy people, if you're looking for a place to take brunch you might somehow be lucky.

Apart from waiting from 1 hour and 20 mins outside the place is good and the food is good. The ambience is a bit like a coffee shop no music in the background and people whispering.

I took the brioche perdue mouth watering and tasty with salted caramel, this is my to go in such places

Would do it again but have to avoid the long wait!", 'rating': '3', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': 'What a complete gem!  Best family oriented place we ate in Paris or London.  A must stop for breakfast, lunch, or light dinner in Paris.', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': 'One of the best brunch in Paris. The staff is super friendly and caring. Food is original and very tasty. Service is fast! Location is very pink and girly 😬', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': 'Amazing atmosphere with food that will make your tastebuds feel magical. If you are looking for a breakfast that’s next level please go here. Staff is very pleasant!!!', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}]

name: Wakanda factory Paris nation
reviews: [{'author': '', 'text': 'Round of applause 🙌 this place blew my mind. Firstly the food. 10/10 flavourful, well cooked and huge portions. I have never seen so much ripe plantain in my life. Juicy and just so on point. The decor was fitting, well done and tasteful. I feel to return to Paris just for this food.', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': 'Quaint, vibrant, and intimate restaurant that is full of Afro Flavor. A bit of heat, salt, acidity, balanced to perfection. My experience with Bakary the host was exceptional, he ensured I received the highest quality of service. I will definitely return to this restaurant and recommend you try their numerous meal selections!', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': 'I was in Paris for 4 days and I casually found this place. I ordered dinner twice: soooo good. Big portions, very tasty, cool place and also not expansive! Recommend it!!!!', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': 'Tasty food and big serving portions.', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': 'Welcoming place with easy going vibes. They serve big portion of delicious food', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}]

name: Tableaux Paris
reviews:
[{'author': '', 'text': 'Loved the creativity & presentation, the freshness of the products! The easiness to order! Will definitely recommend it around me and order more again!!!! Thank you!', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': 'Tableaux Paris enhanced a surprise birthday a few days before the event with 2 magnificent buffets. The food was delicious and in good quantity.
The very easy commercial relationship with the teams and the conscientious implementation work (protection of floors, perfect restoration of the work space and respect of time commitments).
I highly recommend this caterer for your small or large events. The guests were all amazed.', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': 'Overall disappointed with this NORDSTRÖM tray. If the quality of the products is excellent, the quantity of cheese and salmon is really poor. It’s basically a very nice platter of dried fruits (quantity of dried figs and dried apricots) with a berry cream…
I let Internet users compare the photo of the site with that of the tray received and look for the county and the salmon. 56€ all the same!', 'rating': '2', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': 'Original and luxurious (beautiful box, beautiful bag for what they call "Haute fromagerie". Not much choice in the store. Quite expensive. The hazelnut gingerbread goat cheese was very good.', 'rating': '4', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': "We took Tableaux for the catering part of my son's baptism and I can tell you that everything was absolutely PERFECT!!!
The guests were amazed by both the beauty of the buffet and the quality of the products tasted.
I would add that the entire team is extremely kind and professional. Logistics is simple, reliable, fluid.
In short, I recommend with your eyes closed.", 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}]

name: Fay’si Tis
reviews: [{'author': '', 'text': 'Oh my god! These cookies made my day! Possibly the best cookies in Paris. Mine was still warm and so soft. Just amazing, great price as well! I will come here all the time now.', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': 'Warm and cozy atmosphere. Cookie has a perfect gooeyness and sweetness. C‘est bon!', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': 'The cookies are absolutely amazing! The taste, the size and the texture on the top cookie level. There are also delicious juices.', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': 'i had an amazing experience here!! i got a chocolat chaud ultime vanille and it was extraordinarily good! the staff is very nice, they offered me a cookie and omg let me tell you i am going to go there often✨', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}, {'author': '', 'text': 'Excellent cookies. Really well crafted, delicious and priced at 2.50 each.', 'rating': '5', 'date_published': None, 'author_profile_url': '', 'lang': ''}]
